  <brief_title>The Effect of Melatonin on Cognitive Function in Patients Diagnosed With Mild Cognitive Impairment</brief_title>
  <acronym>MCI</acronym>
  <official_title>The Effect of Melatonin on Memory and Other Cognitive Function in Patients Diagnosed With Mild Cognitive Impairment (MCI): A Placebo- Controlled Study.</official_title>
